    <item>
      <title>[工具] Typora</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/typora/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/typora/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] Typora</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="行内latex的行间形式">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%a1%8c%e5%86%85latex%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%8c%e9%97%b4%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f"></a>
行内latex的行间形式
</h2><p><code>\displaystyle</code>: $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to x_0}$</p>
<h2 id="typora-plugin">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#typora-plugin"></a>
typora-plugin
</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/obgnail/typora_plugin">https://github.com/obgnail/typora_plugin</a></p>
<h3 id="1-自动编号">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e7%bc%96%e5%8f%b7"></a>
1. 自动编号
</h3><p>关闭</p>
<h3 id="2-快捷键中心">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83"></a>
2. 快捷键中心
</h3><p>ctrl+m: 添加mark</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="k">const</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">window</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">getSelection</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">toString</span><span class="p">();</span> <span class="n">document</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execCommand</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;insertText&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="bp">false</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="err">?</span> <span class="err">`</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">mark</span><span class="o">&gt;$</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">mark</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">`</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&lt;mark&gt;&lt;/mark&gt;&#39;</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>ctrl+n: 添加颜色span</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="k">const</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">window</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">getSelection</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">toString</span><span class="p">();</span> <span class="n">document</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execCommand</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;insertText&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="bp">false</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="err">?</span> <span class="err">`</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">span</span> <span class="n">style</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;color:red;&#34;</span><span class="o">&gt;$</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">span</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">`</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&lt;span style=&#34;color:red;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#39;</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>ctrl+shift+t: 插入hugo的front_matter</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-21首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-21</p>]]>
      </description>
      
